    Op -->|insertRear| IR1{isFull?}
    IR1 -->|Yes| IR2[Reject: Overflow]
    IR1 -->|No| IR3[Increment rear with wrap]
    IR3 --> IR4[Place element at rear]

    Op -->|deleteFront| DF1{isEmpty?}
    DF1 -->|Yes| DF2[Reject: Underflow]
    DF1 -->|No| DF3[Read element at front]
    DF3 --> DF4[Increment front with wrap]

    Op -->|deleteRear| DR1{isEmpty?}
    DR1 -->|Yes| DR2[Reject: Underflow]
    DR1 -->|No| DR3[Read element at rear]
    DR3 --> DR4[Decrement rear with wrap]

    IF4 --> End[Return to Menu]
    IR4 --> End
    DF4 --> End
    DR4 --> End
```

