### ✍️ Model Solution for Q.B(b) — 7 marks

**Addition (3 marks):**

$$\begin{aligned}
P(x) + Q(x) &= (3x^3 + 2x + 5) + (x^2 - 4) \\
&= 3x^3 + x^2 + 2x + 1
\end{aligned}$$

**Multiplication (4 marks):**

$$\begin{aligned}
P(x) \times Q(x) &= (3x^3 + 2x + 5)(x^2 - 4) \\
&= 3x^3(x^2 - 4) + 2x(x^2 - 4) + 5(x^2 - 4) \\
