#### 🔹 Model Solution for (a) — 7 Marks

**Three deletion cases (4.5 marks):**

1. **Leaf node (no children):** Simply remove the node and set the parent's pointer to NULL. → `free(node); return NULL;`

2. **Node with one child:** Replace the node with its only child. → `parent->link = node->left (or right); free(node);`

3. **Node with two children:** Find the **in-order successor** (smallest node in right sub-tree) OR **in-order predecessor** (largest in left sub-tree). Copy its data into the target node, then recursively delete the successor/predecessor.

