        [38,27,43,3]              [9,82,10]
        /         \               /       \
    [38,27]     [43,3]        [9,82]    [10]
    /   \       /    \        /    \
 [38] [27]  [43]   [3]    [9]    [82]
```

**Theoretical Steps:**
- Total comparisons: $n \log_2 n = 7 \times \lceil \log_2 7 \rceil = 7 \times 3 = 21$
